timeline.bodyText:
Do we want to deprecate the following?
public abstract HelixZkClient buildZkClient(HelixZkClient.ZkConnectionConfig connectionConfig, HelixZkClient.ZkClientConfig clientConfig)
Or put it another way, user later should not directly create non-real aware zkclient from this factory?

